<a href=about-the-picture.html><img src=MIDAS.GIF align=left width=299 
height=195 alt="" border=0 hspace=10></a> <h1>MIDAS</h1>
<h2>The Medical Informatics and Decision Science Consortium</h2>
<h3>Milwaukee, Wisconsin, USA</h3>
<br clear=all>
<hr size=5>
The Medical Informatics and Decision Science (MIDAS) Consortium
brings together faculty and students of two major
academic centers in Milwaukee, Wisconsin.
<p>
<a href=http://www.mcw.edu><img src=MCW.GIF alt="" align=left
border=0 hspace=10></a>
<h3><i>MEDICAL COLLEGE OF WISCONSIN</i></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href=http://www.mcw.edu/radiology/info-sci.html>Section of Information and Decision Sciences</a><br>
Department of Radiology
</ul>
<br clear=all>

<p>
<a href=http://www.uwm.edu><img src=UWM.gif alt="" align=left width=84 
height=64 border=0 hspace=18></a>
<h3><i>UNIVERSITY OF WISCONSIN - MILWAUKEE</i></h3>
<ul>
<li>Artificial Intelligence Laboratory<br>
<a href="http://www.cs.uwm.edu/">Department of Electrical Engineering
and Computer Science</a>
</ul>
<br clear=all>

